creator: Ashish Chauhan
results.description: AC Patel from Gujarat was caught with a Pakistani passport at Delhi airport after being deported from the US. He had used fraudulent documents provided by human traffickers in Dubai. Patel now faces serious charges, including impersonation and misuse of a passport.

results.title: Chamoli avalanche: Last missing worker's body recovered after 2 days of extensive efforts; death toll reaches 8
creator: TOI News Desk
results.description: The Army on Sunday afternoon recovered the body of the eighth missing worker from the Mana avalanche incident, concluding the rescue operation. A total of 54 workers were trapped when the avalanche struck on February 28. Rescue teams employed thermal imaging, drones, and other equipment to locate survivors and recover bodies.
